## Challenges

One problem I ran into was handling sleep times that go past midnight. At first, the math didn’t work right. I fixed it in `calculate_duration_hours()` by adding 24 hours when the wake time is earlier than the sleep time.

Another issue was getting the input rows to update correctly when the number of nights changed. I handled this in `generate_nights()` by rebuilding the rows while keeping the data that was already entered.

